headline: Union Pacific Corporation CFO Jennifer Hamann and Executive Vice President – Operations Eric Gehringer to Address the J.P. Morgan 2025 Industrials Conference
summary: OMAHA, Neb., March 04, 2025--Jennifer Hamann, executive vice president and chief financial officer, and Eric Gehringer, executive vice president – Operations, of Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE: UNP) will address the J.P. Morgan 2025 Industrials Conference on Tuesday, March 11, 2025, at 8:15 a.m. ET.
